column5: Looks like i wont be seeing the regulars April 4th. I just did a what the hell too when i saw the e-mail.  Luckily i saw some of you guys last Thursday at BassCity.  http://www.gagnonsports.com/yardsale.html

Lot's to be added yet, the Pile of rods around my desk is unreal...lot's of Daiwa, St Croix, Shimano  and other goodies to be added. Lot's of cheaper discount items but some better gear it yet to come  Tones of those lures btw, Excalibur, Cotton Cordell, there are a few containers of $5 Rapalas to come also.
